it.unimi.dsi.fastutil.ints

Class Int2BooleanAVLTreeMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.unimi.dsi.fastutil.ints.AbstractInt2BooleanFunction
      • it.unimi.dsi.fastutil.ints.AbstractInt2BooleanMap
        • it.unimi.dsi.fastutil.ints.AbstractInt2BooleanSortedMap
          • it.unimi.dsi.fastutil.ints.Int2BooleanAVLTreeMap
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Function<java.lang.Integer,java.lang.Boolean>, Int2BooleanFunction, Int2BooleanMap, Int2BooleanSortedMap, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.util.Map<java.lang.Integer,java.lang.Boolean>, java.util.SortedMap<java.lang.Integer,java.lang.Boolean>

    public class Int2BooleanAVLTreeMap
extends AbstractInt2BooleanSortedMap
implements java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable
    A type-specific AVL tree map with a fast, small-footprint implementation.

    The iterators provided by the views of this class are type-specific bidirectional iterators. Moreover, the iterator returned by iterator() can be safely cast to a type-specific list iterator.
